{"type": "article", "id": 3512, "title": "Cire Trudon 2014圣诞香氛蜡烛", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-13T08:06:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232925tZU7XwBufhP1rCgL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t法国皇室百年香氛品牌 Cire Trudon 最近推出了他们的 2014 圣诞香氛蜡烛，3 款不同的香味分别被命名为「Bethléem」、「Gabriel 」与「Nazareth」。Bethléem 款由琥珀、胡椒、藏红花、豆蔻以及雪松调制而成，Gabriel 款含有雪松、栗子、白桦木材与苔藓组成，Nazareth 款则融合了肉桂、丁香与波旁香草的味道。3 款香氛蜡烛被放入手工吹制的玻璃罐中，罐子被施以红蓝绿 3 种不同的色彩，内部是用金银两色的锡纸加以装饰。Cire Trudon 此番的圣诞系列提供 9.5 盎司、28 盎司以及 105 盎司 3 种规格，定价 105－550 美元不等，<a href=\"https://www.ciretrudon.com/en/shop/fragrance-of-the-month-classic-candles-bethleem-classic,102.php\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232922YuFvPRlmWS94BgAi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052329238jdwsg4WQx2EXeGV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232923CWk7PYogXpRv4h1D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232924LX0xIepfmFZ2dGgc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232924mSKHqXWYlh91Qy7C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}